{"tid":2457056,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾千人抗議擴警權　破壞警局兼燒警車","createTime":"2021-03-22T11:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T11:07:53.000Z","uid":283837,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2fe2726a2a29a5ff18ce6afe8946cf7e2934002a","tid":2457056,"uid":283837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:03:42.000Z","msg":"英國國會早前通過部分由內政大臣彭黛玲推動的《警察、罪案、判罪與法庭法案》，令警方更易禁止可能引起重大混亂的示威，引發部分市民不滿，抗議警方擴大警權。西南部的布里斯托爾周日（21日）有過千名民眾示威，隨後更演變成衝突。有示威者焚燒警車，至少兩名警員受傷骨折。<br />\n示威者無視新冠疫情的限聚令到布里斯托爾市中心抗議，有人向警察投擲煙花爆竹，並打碎警局的玻璃窗，又在外牆塗鴉。警方斥責本來和平的示威活動「被少數人轉變為騷亂」，又證實示威中有兩輛警車着火，一名警官手臂骨折，另一人肋骨骨折。彭黛玲表示事件不可接受。<br />\n《警察、罪案、判罪與法庭法案》加強警方的執法權限，可限制集會的開始和結束時間、設置音量限制等，違法者可能會被處以最高2,500英鎊（約2.6萬港元）的罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210322/mobile/bkn-20210322061520389-0322_00992_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fintnews%2F20210322%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20210322061520389-0322_00992_001.html&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXMQbtkMcGro9tlpYeKwNq%2B0%3D&h=3774ff68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210322/mobile/bkn-20210322061520389-0322_00992_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9a6208e68ce0f8367377cc6fdd54083809f115ea","tid":2457056,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:05:32.000Z","msg":"樓主紅媒轉貼師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZ8qRbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZ8qRbL.jpg&h=3fbe992f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5f8OYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5f8OYr.jpg&h=ac0b9151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwgjVDr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnwgjVDr.jpg&h=e2cf6d7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0897436c35022f784a124b1333e7cc197045360","tid":2457056,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike